2. Changelog
------------
This is a non-exhaustive (but still near complete) changelog for
JAuthTools. Our thanks to all those people who've contributed bug reports and
code fixes.


Legend:

* -> Security Fix
# -> Bug Fix
+ -> Addition
^ -> Change
- -> Removed
! -> Note


19-Nov-2007 Sam Moffatt
! Preparing for release of JAuthTools 1.0.6 and JLogger 1.0.1
# Fixed issue with iconv param in Joomla! LDAP
# Fixed issue with Use Global not overwriting params (resetting)
# Fixed issue with SSO bailout when user is found but shouldn't be created
^ Added more JLogger entries
^ Added anti user demotion option for Sync Plugin
^ Moved a whole heap of params around to look more consistent
! Added a CHANGELOG file